Fun video by @anywhere_aerials
„Éª„Éª„Éª
Tuning the equipment in the studios, before going on set for the 1st shooting day of "Hellboy III". Everything worked as expected, solid and smooth. Having such huge air time with this rig, carrying Arri Alexa Mini, Masterprime lenses and full FIZ control is a big advantage on set. It allows us to find the right start position, precisely frame the shot, shoot it and do second and third take if needed... all this comfort, without landing and low voltage stress. 
Its a MASSIVE bird.
.
.
Thanks again to the guys from @bfdsystems for their support all the time in the right time, even in their days off. Big ups @maxwell_tubman .
